Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那其他人就隨便決定咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預選賽這玩意就趕緊輕松拿下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年一定要向靜岡的富士崎高中報仇才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以全勝成績拿下全國冠軍!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:04:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸…諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼中只有遠方的話 當心腳下被絆倒哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啦是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個交上去吧 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你可能已經覺得膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今年我們也會帶你去近江神宮的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 現在宣布決賽的順序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北央學園 甘糟同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞澤高中 西田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北央學園 龍崎同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞澤高中 大江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北央學園 木梨同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞澤高中 真島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北央學園 宅間同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞澤高中 駒野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北央學園 須藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞澤高中 綾瀨同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全猜中了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩羅牌…真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「對不起」呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「對不起」呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經說了「抱歉」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說「對不起」就不原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請將牌擺好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面進入暗記時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這人怎麼搞的啊
