Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:20.10,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay0.13\c&HCCA28B&\an5\fs30\pos(1200,385)}我是千早。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:20.10,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay0.13\c&HCCA28B&\an5\fs30\pos(1095,401)}新，生日那天的郵件謝謝。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:20.10,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay0.13\c&HCCA28B&\an5\fs30\pos(1065,441)}沒想到新會記得呢，嚇我一跳。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:24.61,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&HC28B6F&\pos(294,85)}東京都預賽的聯系來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:24.61,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBE8C6B&\fs30\pos(1177,439)}成功了——!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:24.61,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBE8C6B&\fs30\pos(1110,484)}凑齊了五個隊員，可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:24.61,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBE8C6B&\fs30\pos(1096,530)}参加大會了! 今天把材料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:26.48,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(334,90)}瑞澤高中的第一次勝利!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:26.48,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(1191,482)}贏啦——!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:26.48,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(1148,528)}太一和肉包小子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:26.48,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(1194,571)}狀態都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:28.36,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(252,91)}分組賽勝出咯!
